#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.groupby.GroupBy.transform.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.groupby.GroupBy.transform"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:1 of
msgid ""
"Call function producing a like-indexed DataFrame on each group and return"
" a DataFrame having the same indexes as the original object filled with "
"the transformed values"
msgstr ""
"对每个分组调用生成具有相同索引的 DataFrame 的函数，并返回一个与原始对象"
"具有相同索引且填充了转换值的 DataFrame"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:5 of
msgid "Function to apply to each group."
msgstr "应用到每个分组的函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:7 of
msgid "Specify dtypes of returned DataFrames. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回的 DataFrames 的数据类型。详见“注意事项”。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:9 of
msgid "Specify dtype of returned Series. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回的 Series 的数据类型。详见“注意事项”。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:11 of
msgid "Specify name of returned Series. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回的 Series 的名称。详见“注意事项”。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:13 of
msgid "Whether infer dtypes when dtypes or output_type is not specified."
msgstr "当未指定 dtypes 或 output_type 时是否推断数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:15 of
msgid "Positional arguments to pass to func"
msgstr "传递给 func 的位置参数"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:16 of
msgid "Keyword arguments to be passed into func."
msgstr "传递给 func 的关键字参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:20 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`DataFrame.groupby.apply`, :py:obj:`DataFrame.groupby.aggregate`,"
" :py:obj:`DataFrame.transform`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:23
#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:40 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:24 of
msgid ""
"Each group is endowed the attribute 'name' in case you need to know which"
" group you are working on."
msgstr "每个分组都会被赋予 'name' 属性，以便你知道当前处理的是哪个分组。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:27 of
msgid "The current implementation imposes three requirements on f:"
msgstr "当前实现对 f 提出了三项要求："

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:29 of
msgid ""
"f must return a value that either has the same shape as the input "
"subframe or can be broadcast to the shape of the input subframe. For "
"example, if `f` returns a scalar it will be broadcast to have the same "
"shape as the input subframe."
msgstr ""
"f 必须返回一个与输入子帧形状相同或可以广播为输入子帧形状的值。例如，如果 "
"`f` 返回一个标量，则它将被广播为与输入子帧相同的形状。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:33 of
msgid ""
"if this is a DataFrame, f must support application column-by-column in "
"the subframe. If f also supports application to the entire subframe, then"
" a fast path is used starting from the second chunk."
msgstr ""
"如果这是一个 DataFrame，f 必须支持在子帧中逐列应用。如果 f 还支持应用于"
"整个子帧，则从第二个分块开始使用快速路径。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:36 of
msgid ""
"f must not mutate groups. Mutation is not supported and may produce "
"unexpected results."
msgstr "f 不得修改分组。修改操作不受支持，可能会产生意外结果。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:41 of
msgid ""
"When deciding output dtypes and shape of the return value, MaxFrame will "
"try applying ``func`` onto a mock grouped object, and the transform call "
"may fail."
msgstr ""
"在决定输出数据类型和返回值形状时，MaxFrame 会尝试将 ``func`` 应用于模拟的"
"分组对象，此时 transform 调用可能会失败。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:45 of
msgid ""
"For DataFrame output, you need to specify a list or a pandas Series as "
"``dtypes`` of output DataFrame. ``index`` of output can also be "
"specified."
msgstr ""
"对于 DataFrame 输出，你需要将一个列表或 pandas Series 指定为输出 "
"DataFrame 的 ``dtypes``。也可以指定输出的 ``index``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:48 of
msgid ""
"For Series output, you need to specify ``dtype`` and ``name`` of output "
"Series."
msgstr "对于 Series 输出，你需要指定输出 Series 的 ``dtype`` 和 ``name``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.transform.groupby_transform:52 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

